nl.naturalis.oaipmh.geneious

Interface IAnnotatedDocumentPostProcessor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DnaExtractPostProcessor

    public interface IAnnotatedDocumentPostProcessor
    A IAnnotatedDocumentPostProcessor allows for the manipulation of data just before it is converted to XML. Post processors are applied after all filters have been applied and after the remaining AnnotatedDocument instances have been converted to JAXB objects representing the <record> elements underneath the <OAI-PMH> root element. The post processor allows you to manipulate these JAXB objects just before they are serialized to XML.
    Author:
    Ayco Holleman
